Package: EnsembleRandomForests
Title: Ensemble Random Forests
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Zachary",
           family = "Siders",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "zachary.siders@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0798-9515"))
Description: This package implements Ensemble Random Forests from Siders et al.
    (2020) "Ensemble Random Forests as a tool for modeling rare occurrences" in
    Endangered Species Research. Functions are provided to execute the ERF model on
    a dataset, adjust model parameters, as well as summarize and visualize model
    performance and predictions.
URL: https://github.com/zsiders/EnsembleRandomForests/
